#Input Function explained
#The input function allows data to be entered into a program
#Examples are below

name = input("Enter your name (Then press enter): ") 
print("Hello, " , name) 

colour = input("Enter your favourite colour (Then press enter): ")
print("Your favourite colour is ", colour)

age = int(input("Enter your age, then press enter"))
print("Your age is ", age)

print("your name is ", name, "and your favourite colour is ", colour, "and your age is ",age,)
